data.description: Offer deadline Monday (2/12) at 2pm.  Meticulously renovated with no detail overlooked. Gleaming refinished hardwood floors throughout. The open eat-in kitchen, dining, and living room make this house perfect for entertaining inside, while the expansive deck, large fenced backyard, and fire pit make for the ideal outdoor gatherings. The oversized primary bedroom included a sitting area and dual closets. The second upstairs bedroom is large enough for kids or guests. The basement is the perfect place to relax, with a built-in bar and spacious family room. Both downstairs bedrooms include large egress windows for additional light.  Bonus extra large backyard shed is the perfect place for hobbies or extra storage.  New roof, gutters, front and back door (2021) New Trex Deck with aluminum rails (2022) New siding and paint (2022) New AC (2023) Floors Refinished and Carpet Replaced (2024) Convenient to schools, restaurants, and shopping.
